rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0001
rows.name:
Huh, there's a massive ship over at
the port!

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0002
rows.name:
Ah, yes. That would be the
Superbian flagship.

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0004
rows.name:
Makes sense. You want to make
a show of your nation's might, do
it with a big boat.

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0005
rows.name:
Why don't we all board? It'd be a
shame to leave some of us waiting
outside.

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh, no need, really! I'm terrible with
stuffy environments. And all that noble
food doesn't sit well with me...

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0007
rows.name:
We could have the cooks recreate
some your country's cuisine, if it
please you?

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0008
rows.name:
I appreciate the sentiment Hugo
but I'll pass. Come on, Kasumi!

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0010
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]She's not going to get used to it any
time soon with that attitude...
